Class PlanningDetailsItem

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    public class PlanningDetailsItem
extends javafx.scene.layout.AnchorPane
    This class represents an item of the PlanningDetails list. It describes a step of the planning: the departure time, arrival time, time of delivery (after eventually waiting for the opening), the status (possible, impossible) and of course the concerned waypoint. It also contains buttons to add a a waypoint just before this one or to remove the current waypoint.
